<h1>@starlib_pkg_button_templates.horizontal_button_image</h1>
<p>starlib_pkg_button_templates.horizontal_button_image is a dynamic pre-made image template for the horizontal button. Used in starlib_pkg_button_templates.horizontal_button_template</p>
<span class="load-content" data-file="docs/package_button/button_templates/horizontal_button_template">@starlib_pkg_button_templates.horizontal_button_template</span>
<div id="important-info-container" class="important-info">
    <div class="important-info-bar"></div>
    <div class="important-info-content">
        <h3>Info</h3>
        <p>This image element supports adding a background to the image panel, as well as customizing the size of the right margin from the main content of the horizontal button.</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="image-container">
    <div class="image-item">
        <p>Without enabled image panel background</p>
        <img src="assets/pages/button_templates/horizontal_img.png" alt="Image 1">
    </div>
